OL,6,FThe regulator's investigation
OL,7,Funcovered failings in the planning,
OL,8,Fmonitoring and supervision of the work.
OL,10,FEarlier this month, Network Rail was
OL,11,Ffined #3.75 million after two workers
OL,12,Fwere struck and killed by a train at
OL,13,FMargam, near Port Talbot in July 2019.
OL,15,FRichard Hines, ORR's HM Chief
OL,16,FInspector of Railways, said: "Our
OL,17,Findustry's track workers play a
OL,18,Fcrucial role in delivering a safe
OL,19,Frailway for passengers and users of
OL,20,Fthe system, often working in
OL,21,Fchallenging and difficult conditions.
