OL,6,F"It's essential that they are also
OL,7,Fprotected from harm.
OL,9,F"In a period when we also remembered
OL,10,Fthose who lost their lives at Margam
OL,11,Fin 2019, let us keep our focus on
OL,12,Freducing the risks faced by our
OL,13,Fpeople."
OL,15,FEllie Burrows, Network Rail's managing
OL,16,Fdirector for the southern region, said
OL,17,Fthe incident which killed Mr Byrne
OL,18,F"should never have happened on our
OL,19,Frailway", and the company is "deeply
OL,20,Fsorry for what happened".
