OL,6,FShe went on: "Since this tragic event
OL,7,Fwe've continued to take significant
OL,8,Fsteps to improve safety.
OL,10,F"Our track worker safety programme has
OL,11,Falmost entirely eliminated the need
OL,12,Ffor colleagues working on the railway
OL,13,Fwhen trains are running.
OL,15,F"We have done this by carrying out
OL,16,Fmaintenance work at different times,
OL,17,Fusing alternative technology and we
OL,18,Fcontinue to examine our planned work
OL,19,Fto keep our colleagues safe.
